review_blob: This beer changed my opinion on hoppy beers. Used to never be a fan but my palate is clearly changing now. A draft beer fav now.
Bought a multi-pack of Big Rock (as I like to try different beers) and found this. I actually tried it last as I wasnt sure what to expect but was very pleased.
One of my go to beers. Always refreshing, great tasting, and the big glass still gets peoples attention.
